WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
The real estate downturn, I think, is the really the primary factor causing China's cyclical economic downturn in the last few years,

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:15.000
because the property sector really went beyond property, unlike in other countries, which all had their ups and downs in property,

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:23.000
because it represented two core pillars of the economy, a shadow fiscal system and a shadow financial system.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Something like 90% of local government debt is tied to real estate, and 70% of national debt is tied to real estate.
